name: Aztec entity 55 - "Mitotiqui"
description: Entity 55/100 in this collection of aztec kaleidoscopic deities, imbuing recoloured restorations of aztec sacred texts by female artist Quetzecoatlia with sentient energies. Kaleidoscopes 1-54 are available on Opensea!   This benevolent entity is named Mitotiqui, a nahuatl word meaning dancer.
